Package arrayGenerator

Interface ArrayGenerator

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ListingGenerator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CleverRandomListingGenerator, CleverRandomListingGeneratorTimer, RandomListingGenerator, SimpleRandomListingGenerator, SimpleRandomListingGeneratorTimer, SortedListingGenerator
    public interface ArrayGenerator
    Defines the interface for classes that generate arrays of ints

    The constructor for implementations of this class should generate an array of ints

    This is an interface, and specifies the signature(s) of method(s) that should be implemented in (a) separate class(es). See the tester class for tests of this interface's properties.

    Version:
    September 2019
    Author:
    Hugh Osborne
